name: Irregularshed.github.io
tagline: One day I'll have a site
body:
### Oh hai
So, it turns out that you can create a whole website on Github without even hitting your own command line! Given I've been dragging my feet for _ages_ this is probably a good place to start.

The other handy thing is I can update this from pretty much anywhere...
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
